                <span style="font-size:0.75rem; border:1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius:16px; padding:5px 10px;">🔊 Listen</span>
                <span style="font-size:0.75rem; background:#eff6ff; border:1px solid #3b82f6; color:#1d4ed8; border-radius:16px; padding:5px 10px;">🎤 Speak</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="landing-section" data-reveal>
          <h2 style="text-align:center; font-size:1.6rem; margin-bottom: 6px;">A lesson is a path, not a quiz.</h2>
          <p style="text-align:center; color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--m-ink) 60%, white); margin-bottom: 30px;">Every phrase moves through the same three predictable stones, every time.</p>
          <div class="feature-stone-grid">
            <div class="feature-stone">
              <div class="fs-icon" style="background:var(--pastel-blue);">👀</div>
              <div><h3>1. Listen</h3><p>The phrase is shown and read aloud slowly, with the real-life moment it's used in spelled out plainly.</p></div>
